### Add a payment to an order
POST http://localhost:8080/api/commandes/3/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "montant": 1500,
  "typePaiement": "ESPECES",
  "reference": "RECU-001"
}

### Update payment status to ENCAISSE (counts toward remaining amount)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/commandes/payments/5/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "statut": "ENCAISSE",
  "dateEncaissement": "2025-11-26T00:00:00.000+00:00"
}
